Django-Headline
===============

Complex of tags and filters for easy replacement of text
with alternative font faces. For browsers, who doesn`t
support it by themselves.


1. Copyright
2. Regards
3. Reqirements
4. Installation and configuration
5. Usecase
6. Known improvements


